{"tid":1245030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挑戰批發及零售界有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-06-20T07:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T17:43:33.000Z","uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7015292f06bc1def981219435b41d10c5fb19ba4","tid":1245030,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"作為一個sales，功能組別好似一直都唔關自己事，自己又無咩特長<br />\n<br />\n見呢排巴絲都諗緊計攻陷功能組別，就諗緊自己有咩可以幫到手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YiLdO2J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYiLdO2J.png&h=2a572d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5nr82K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5nr82K.png&h=b35c6714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要做呢咁多個會是旦一個嘅會員先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後發現我可以加入HKRMA (零售管理協會），呢個會應該由旺中到金鐘嘅sales都聽過<br />\n<br />\n入會費1000，不過要做功能界別選民嘅要求係登記前一年都要係會員<br />\n<br />\n雖然1000可以食餐好嘅，不過如果立法會泛民打算挑戰呢個界別（歐諾軒好似參選過），咁就要早d入會了....<br />\n<br />\n糾結中，因為如果呢個界別無人同現任嘅爭（現任係自由黨副主席），咁就變咗選唔到超區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無零售批發巴絲一齊研究吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25df57e3f41ba66f4e09a3cbc3cea99ca5f257e2","tid":1245030,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"有。"},{"pid":"158a5dc8da097f128b00231abbfef0046241159b","tid":1245030,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25df57e3f41ba66f4e09a3cbc3cea99ca5f257e2","tid":1245030,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"有。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"多謝推post<br />\n不過我已經搵咗6位同路人搞工會了<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com%2F&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=f28f1192\" tar